## Guidelines

- Focus on the **in-app frames** in the stacktrace — these are the frames in your application code (not third-party libraries).
- The culprit is usually the topmost in-app frame where the exception originates.
- Make the smallest change that definitively fixes the issue.
- Do not refactor unrelated code or introduce new dependencies unless necessary.
- If the fix requires a test, add it.
